  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps</p><p>Wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 mins)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the<strong> halved cherry tomatoes</strong> with the <strong>chorizo</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed the <strong>yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cherry tomatoes have softened, add the <strong>sliced pepper</strong> with the<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>steamed basmati rice</strong> with the <strong>pitted black olives</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until the rice is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is warmed through, add the <strong>soy sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-one-pot-chorizo-and-tomato-rice/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chorizo & tomato rice</strong> garnished with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> rocket</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
